Overview

[Ch2 23:1](../../../bib/kjv/ch2023.htm#001.md), Jehoiada, having set things
in order, makes Joash king; [Ch2
23:12](../../../bib/kjv/ch2023.htm#012.md), Athaliah is slain; [Ch2
23:16](../../../bib/kjv/ch2023.htm#016.md), Jehoiada restores the worship
of God.

